{"tid":227703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【繼兒動武續集】疑分居妻與33歲仔有染 台漢潛入屋刺殺釀兩死","createTime":"2017-05-03T11:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T14:24:23.000Z","uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"912c39c7389e90253b0948253690f386fc45de91","tid":227703,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"台灣苗栗縣傳出兇案，一名63歲黃姓男子，懷疑分居前妻（59歲）跟兒子（33歲）有染，今天凌晨3時許潛入妻兒位於竹南鎮的住所，持剪刀刺殺熟睡中的妻子及兒子。妻子當場死亡，兒子負傷爬至屋外求救，但送院後仍宣告傷重不治。警方已將黃男拘捕，目前正在問話中。<br />\n<br />\n警方透露，無業的黃男早前在其他地點居住，近日才搬到事發地點，與前妻和兒子同住。目擊的鄰居顏婦稱，當時聽到疑似打架聲音，出門查看時，赫然看到黃男將兒子壓在門外地上，好像拿利器一直朝他身上猛刺好幾下，沒多久其兒子掙脫起身，渾身是血、負傷往巷口逃跑。黃男隨後猛追，他的兒子已不支倒臥在水溝裏。顏婦嚇得趕緊入屋致電報警。她說，這對母子在這邊住了20多年，聽說當時是因丈夫家暴，母子才逃離南部住家北上躲藏，但最近發現其前夫突然前來同住約1個月，沒想到竟然發生命案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170503&amp;guid=56644503&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170503%26guid%3D56644503%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=38917fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170503%26guid%3D56644503%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=7eba93f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170503&amp;guid=56644503&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"313d0a2581c5da4373c3a7fedeaf0ae082d9c991","tid":227703,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ac21856025015df2b8f536d14e537e5494a41c","tid":227703,"uid":107866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"台灣又得一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f43c87e3542356d20a04204f8844de4fc83cc9","tid":227703,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ff073de97cdcc56c6ad599232463108a04f77","tid":227703,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"台灣超美麗的風景是人！"},{"pid":"9b67687cfe6f9f12ea27f139dfbbcd309c5c52fe","tid":227703,"uid":3272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"繼兒動母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66a9ae4014e99276b476e59664b42954a65a839","tid":227703,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"59同33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞錯咗咪好冤枉"},{"pid":"0ca8cfb5f9e9d008448b2d2de221b8c5da20c541","tid":227703,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼兒動母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425695bfd9b1d02978c1e9e203c5a3b4771cd638","tid":227703,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>59同33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞錯咗咪好冤枉</blockquote><br />\n唔信囉"},{"pid":"39c72b137eaa84ab0b335de3fd35994292bb6e5f","tid":227703,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"59歲 (驅風)"}]}